Mobile app for travel industry solution

Why let people stand in queues when they can find all the solutions sitting at homes comfortably on your Travel App. Here we are providing you with incredible solutions related to the travel industry that can make your travel application shine.

Hotel booking system

Everyone travels and needs some space that is full of comfort and nice to live in. With the best comparisons of different hotels based on the reviews and star ratings, we help you to choose your someplace nice in your budget. We at youssefghamry provide you with a planned and well-compared hotel booking system.

Ticket booking system

To travel from one place to another, one needs to decide the mode of transportation and check whether it fits in their budget or not. youssefghamry offers you the best and an easy ticket booking system to and from any place in the world.

Vehicle rental system

With the onset of COVID-19, it has become very difficult for every person to trust any vehicle rental companies in terms of health, security, and privacy. Hire travel app/web developers in India like youssefghamry that makes it easy by providing you with a safe and secure rental system for vehicles.

GPS-based location services

youssefghamry believes that your customer can feel safe in renting vehicles and other services. Hence we need to provide them with a trusted and open system that they are familiar with and providing GPS-based location services is the best thing.

Currency converter

youssefghamry is not only concerned with you traveling in the same country, but also in different countries. So we give you an option on our website for currency conversion that is, we develop a code for you wherein you can convert one currency into another to check its corresponding value according to the latest currency exchange rates.

Complete travel guide

Wherever one goes, he needs a guide. Hence, youssefghamry gives you the option of a travel guide in the application. This feature provides you all the information regarding the places the user wants to visit, the transportation, restaurants, accommodation, and activities.

Secure payment gateway integration

youssefghamry encrypts the card details and ensures the safe passing of details to the bank. We simplify how the merchants integrate the necessary software. All the bank details are secured so users can fully trust the app.

Easy to use Admin control panel

Hence, you can see that youssefghamry can layout an app for you with all the features from the beginning to the end for travel, be it related to business trips or family vacations. The application has a smooth Admin control panel and has an easy to use interface.

Travel Mobile App Features

People are considering to hire travel app developers like youssefghamry that brings forth the following features in the app. We try our best to provide you with the best services. The travel audience goes crazy when they get to experience such amazing features in the travel application. Let's look over it-

  • Travel
  • Travel destinations

Trip planning

In the current times, we provide you with the best places with reviews of people and star ratings, hence helping you to plan the best trips. We make it easy for the customers to find places worth going in their budget itself and making their trip memorable.

Travel map

youssefghamry helps you create an app that acts as a travel map to the users. It guides the users to locate places by giving them information about tourist spots and landmarks. It also tells about the travel routes to the tourists. It acts as a portable travel map.

Travel tracking

Wherever the user goes, our app provides the feature of travel tracking with the use of GPS based location services. With features like these, the users feel more comfortable, safe, and secure. It helps the users to locate themselves and also help them find the places to visit.

Travel checklist

We at youssefghamry bring you a feature of travel checklist wherein we provide you with a list so you can maintain a checklist of the already visited places and create memories in more new places. It is a feature that builds an urge inside the hearts of travel lovers to go out and see the new places where they have never gone.

Tourist guide

youssefghamry will help you create an app that would be a guide for all the tourists at new places. It will help you lead your way to unknown destinations of interest and fun according to your interest. It takes you to the most important destinations that you must visit.

Tour booking

The app will also help the users in booking the tour according to their plan, stay, and budget. They can pre-plan all their tour visits and hence have a smooth and proper vacation or business tour.

Vehicle booking

youssefghamry can develop an app for you that not only help you rent the vehicle according to your choice, rates, number of members but will also take care of your safety and security at all times. The GPS-based location services feature is also provided by us that makes the users feel more secure.

Hotel booking

The travel app developed takes care of the bookings in the hotels and restaurants you choose. The bookings will be assured and, nobody can cancel it without your approval. It will be a 24*7 hotel booking service.

Travel agent feature

The app would behave like a travel agent to you. It will help you find your way to new and the best must-visit places and also lets you book your tour in advance. Hence, your full trip is all managed by the application. The pre-planned trip would help you in being organized and, therefore, there would be no last-minute issues.

Trip organizer

The travel audience would love a virtual trip organizer. It books your travel tickets, your hotel, restaurants, must-visit places, vehicles to rent, guides you throughout the tour, and has a travel agent feature. Hence, it organizes your trip very well.

Places to visit

youssefghamry delivers an app that tells about the must-visit places. We provide a travel checklist feature, where users can make a smart list of places they want to visit and the places that they can prefer according to their budget.

Travel news

All news related to the travel industry both nationally and internationally, be it about the airplane tickets or any changes in the weather affecting your tour and travel- everything gets updated in the app.

Travel assistant

youssefghamry creates an app that operates as a travel assistant to the users. It assists you at all points of time, be it day or night. It functions as a personal assistant to you, which guides you where to go, how, and when.

Tourist feedback sharing

The most important feature for anyone in any application is that they can share their reviews and feedbacks with everyone so that it could benefit others also.

Flight booking

Not only can you rent vehicles, book hotels, and restaurants, organize your trips, but also book your tickets online for the airplane using the application. It makes the booking of the tickets and confirmation of the booking an easy way for the users.

Travel photography

The users can post their travel photography with the other users on the app itself. It not only is a great feature to showcase your travel photography passion but also can you find your next travel destination from this feature. It helps other users to find the best places in the world that are unrecognized.

Travel videos

The users can post their travel videos from all over the world and share their experiences and thus give reviews for everyone else. It gives you a platform to present your videos in an amazing and creative way.

Live chat

We develop this feature for the people who are planning to travel so that in case of any inquiry, problems, or issues, they can contact the team of the application, and the team could respond to them instantly or as soon as possible.
